> //Four members of MTF-59 (hereby referred to as Ghost-1, Ghost-2, Ghost-3, & Ghost-4[[footnote]] Spiritual Medium, Imogen Calloway [[/footnote]]) arrive at Site-74 at 2:45am on January 23, 2021. This event summary has been compiled using the surviving body cam footage along with the testimony of the remaining member of MTF-59.//
