> **<BEGIN LOG>**
> 
> **3:00:45** Door is unlocked by the newly promoted SCP-7000 lead, Dr. Clemons. MTF-59 enters and begins preparing their ghost hunting equipment. 
> 
> **3:01:12** Clemons locks the doors of Site-74 before entering a nearby security van to watch Site-74 cameras and to keep contact over a handheld radio transceiver. 
> 
> **3:10:52** Investigation officially begins outside of Ian Vance’s former office. Ghost-4 senses minor spirit activity. Spirit Box and EMF reader remain silent. 
> 
> **3:13:04** Office door is approached and opened. MTF-59 enters. Ghost-4 states that she feels “a much stronger ghost presence”, and beginning to remove an item from her belt.[[footnote]] This item was later determined to be Anomalous Item-13, a minor protective charm [[/footnote]] 
> 
> **3:13:05** The office door is slammed open and loud footsteps can be heard. This sudden noise causes Ghost-4 to rush outside, causing the newly loosened item on her belt to fall off. Ghost-1 & -3 rush out of the office. Security camera footage begins to distort, but the image is still mostly visible.  
> 
> **3:13:24** Dr. Clemens attempts contact to no avail. Ghost-4 begins to follow a "ghostly apparition" asking questions with a spirit box as she walks forward, followed by Ghost-1 & -3.
> 
> **3:14:16** Ghost-2 remains in the office with the EMF reader. It flashes a few times before shutting off. Ghost-2 goes to replace the batteries, before finding Anomalous Item-13 which had fallen under the desk.
> 
