> 
> **3:16:02** A large series of cracks are heard as Ghost-3 falls to the floor in a pile of blood[[footnote]] Later examination would prove the cause of death to be blunt force trauma, similar to those caught under rubble doing natural disasters. [[/footnote]]. Ghost-4 begins chanting and is joined by Ghost-1. Ghost-1's chanting turns to screams as the left side of his body begins to cave in, causing blood and viscera to exit his mouth. All cameras in the area shut off simultaneously.
> 
> **3:16:20** Ghost-2 arrives to see Ghost-4 fall to the ground as the chanting stops. [[footnote]] Later D-class testing would show this area to consistently affect the neck and upper chest first.  [[/footnote]]
> 
