> **3:16:28** Ghost-2 finishes his chant before going into shock.
> 
> **3:20:05** Dr. Clemons sends in a medical retrieval team who finds Ghost-2 alive and quickly escorts him to the medical wing of Site-74 for emergency medical care.
> 
