> 
> **Event Outcome:** Ghost-2 survived the initial attack but was found to be suffering from nearly complete body paralysis as several vertebrae in his spine were crushed before the cessation of the SCP-7000 Bludgeoning Event. Interviews utilizing an eye-operated communication device were able to piece together his experience of the event.

Following Bludgeoning Event 7000-1, the current containment procedures went into effect. Due to the aggressive nature of SCP-7000 prior to the event, Imogen Calloway left instructions on effective spiritual practices to help contain SCP-7000.

